oard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif",":)","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/sick.gif",":x","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif",":p","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smokin.gif",":smokin","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tired.gif","|I","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif",":(","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/nerd.gif","8o","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif",":b","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif",":lol","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/embarassed.gif",":o","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif",";)","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/indifferent.gif",":|","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/grin.gif"," >D","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/alien.gif","0]","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/roll.gif",":rollin","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/pimp.gif",":hat","http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif",":evil" );</script><style type="text/css">#textformatting { margin: 3px 0 3px 0;}.insertbutton {font-size: 11px; width: 70px;}.formatbutton {font-size: 11px; width: 25px;}.fontselect {font-size: 11px;}#setfont { margin-left:15px; padding: 3px; background-color: #dcdeed; border: 1px solid #000000; }.fontbutton {font-size: 11px;}#emoticonbox {padding:4px; width:90%;}</style></head><body text=#333333 bgcolor=#666eb0 link=#333366 vlink=#000066 alink=#333366  background=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/background.gif  ><center> <br> <a href=><img src=http://www.myezboard.com/projects/ezboard/ezboard_userimages/vazaellecommunitycenter/images/1pixel.GIF border=0></a>  <table width=95%><tr><td class=headings valign="bottom"><a href="http://www.ezboard.com